{
  "stem": "9156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's a kind of an almost a comical thing when I tell it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't so comical because I thought I would be sended back to the Nazis, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Also, I have to say some little thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we walked through the underground tunnel from the one place to this place, the advances that they do to young girls, amazing, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I never quite understand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But all my life, I seem to have been able to say, 'Oh, leave me alone.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But sometimes I think I was perhaps not pretty enough.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was pretty stupid in that thing, but then they put me into what they called a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think it was in the camp [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mauthausen ?] but I cannot guarantee that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not really underground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's in a police station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to take my glasses away, and I screamed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I can't see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still remember one big policeman said, 'Let her go.'",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, anyhow, I get into that concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is another almost a joke, but it wasn't a joke at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the head officer concentration camp says, 'What do I do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is all men, one woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What's she doing?' 'Well, we have no other place to put her.' So I heard this command, and all the doors that were open had to be closed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to pass by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put me into one room, which was almost as large as this one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They still didn't allow me to read anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very odd.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very different.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
